%% Diagram: Atomic record append — primary-chosen offset, at-least-once
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant C1 as Client 1
    participant C2 as Client 2
    participant P as Primary CS
    participant S as Secondary CS

    Note over C1,S: Both clients append concurrently to the same chunk
    C1->>P: AppendChunk(data1)
    C2->>P: AppendChunk(data2)

    P->>P: If chunk would exceed 64 MB →\npad to chunk boundary, return ChunkFull
    P->>P: Assign offset1, offset2 in serial order

    P->>S: Apply data1 @ offset1
    P->>S: Apply data2 @ offset2
    S-->>P: Acks
    P-->>C1: Success @ offset1
    P-->>C2: Success @ offset2

    Note over C1,S: Failure mid-pipeline → at-least-once retry,\nresulting in defined regions + inconsistent padding
